(1) In [Package.json] There Are Field Called [scripts] I Can Call Any Script Inside It After Running

(2) How To Manage
------------------
==> Create File Called [App.js] Beside [Package.json] File And Have Some Code Like [console.log('Hellow')]

==> Open [Package.json] And Set The [scripts] Field As Showen

	"scripts": {
	    "start": "node App.js" // Start Here Called Entry Point That Program Start Execute From It
	  }
	  
==> Write [npm start] In Command Line You Note That [App.js] Content Is Executed In The Command Line


